1:9 Maze Abayuda baramanuka batera Abanyakanāni bo mu gihugu cy'imisozi miremire, n'ab'ikusi n'abo mu bibaya. 
1:10   
1:11 Bavayo batera abari batuye i Debira (kera i Debira hitwaga i Kiriyatiseferi). 
1:12 Ariko Kalebu aravuga ati “Uzatera i Kiriyatiseferi akahatsinda, nzamushyingira umukobwa wanjye Akisa.” 
1:13 Bukeye Otiniyeli mwene Kenazi murumuna wa Kalebu arahatsinda, nuko ashyingirwa wa mukobwa. 
1:14 Maze uwo mukobwa yegera umugabo we aramuhendahenda ngo asabe se igikingi. Ava ku ndogobe ye, Kalebu aramubaza ati “Urashaka iki?” 
1:15   
1:16  wa Mose, bazamukana na bene Yuda bavuye mu mudugudu w'imikindo, bajya mu butayu bw'i Buyuda buri ikusi ya Arada, baturanayo n'abaho. 
1:17 Bukeye Abayuda bajyana n'Abasimeyoni bene wabo, banesha Abanyakanāni b'abaturage b'i Sefati, baraharimbura rwose. Kandi uwo mudugudu witwaga Horuma. 
1:18 Maze Abayuda batsinda i Gaza bageza ku rugabano rwaho, na Ashikeloni n'urugabano rwaho, na Ekuroni n'urugabano rwaho. 
1:19 Uwiteka yari kumwe n'Abayuda birukana bene igihugu cy'imisozi miremire, ariko ntibabasha kwirukana abo mu bibaya kuko bari bafite amagare y'ibyuma. 
1:20 Kalebu bamuha i Heburoni nk'uko Mose yari yaravuze, yirukanamo bene Anaki uko ari batatu. 
