1:24 Abo batasi babonye umuntu wavaga muri uwo mudugudu baramwinginga bati “Twereke irembo ry'uyu mudugudu tuzakugirira neza.” 
1:25 Uwo mugabo abereka irembo ry'umudugudu, nuko Abayosefu barimbuza abo muri uwo mudugudu inkota, ariko wa mugabo n'abo mu rugo rwe bose barabareka. 
