6:20 Maze marayika w'Imana aramubwira ati “Enda iyi nyama n'utwo dutsima ubishyire hejuru y'iki gitare, usukeho n'umufa wazo.” Nuko abigenza atyo. 
6:21   
6:22   
6:23 Nuko Uwiteka aramubwira ati “Humura, witinya ntupfa.” 
